{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Style Description: Modern, Editorial-Style Collection Showcase
    This style mimics the layout of a high-end digital magazine or lookbook. It uses large, impactful imagery to create an aspirational and brand-focused experience, guiding users towards curated collections rather than individual products.
    
    Key Components Breakdown:
    1. Layout and Structure
    Grid of Feature Cards: The section is built as a grid (in this case, three columns) of large, independent promotional cards.
    
    Significant Rounded Corners: The cards have prominently rounded corners, which gives the design a soft, modern, and friendly feel, contrasting with sharp-edged, traditional layouts.
    
    Generous Gutters: There is clear spacing between each card, which helps them stand out as individual stories or features.
    
    2. The Feature Card
    Each card is a self-contained unit designed to capture attention and drive a single, focused action.
    
    Image as the Background: The entire background of each card is a high-quality, professional photograph.
    
    Photography Style: The images are "editorial" or "lifestyle" in nature. They feature models in relatable contexts or artfully styled product shots (still life), rather than simple product photos on a plain background. This helps to tell a story and sell a feeling, not just an object.
    
    Text Overlay: All text is placed directly on top of the image.
    
    Legibility: To ensure the text is readable against a complex background, it's often placed on a less busy part of the photo. Sometimes, a very subtle, transparent gradient is applied behind the text to increase contrast without being obvious.
    
    Typography: The font is typically a clean, bold, and modern sans-serif. There is a clear hierarchy, with a larger headline to announce the theme (e.g., "Fresh takes on classic frames").
    
    Call-to-Action (CTA) Button:
    
    Style: The button is prominent but fits the overall aesthetic. It's a "pill-shaped" button with fully rounded ends.
    
    Design: It uses a solid color fill (e.g., white or black/dark , use brand colours and make sure to remember its eyewear company  
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-editorial-showcase-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 0 {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.section_background }};
  }

  .ai-editorial-showcase-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.container_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 {{ block.settings.gutter }}px;
  }

  .ai-editorial-showcase-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_desktop }}, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.card_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-editorial-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: {{ block.settings.card_aspect_ratio }};
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-editorial-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .ai-editorial-card-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ai-editorial-card-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0%,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 50%,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, {{ block.settings.overlay_opacity }}) 100%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ai-editorial-card-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: {{ block.settings.content_padding }}px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-editorial-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.title_weight }};
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.title_spacing }}px;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.title_transform }};
  }

  .ai-editorial-card-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtitle_size }}px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.button_spacing }}px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .ai-editorial-card-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: {{ block.settings.button_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.button_padding_horizontal }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.button_font_weight }};
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.button_text_transform }};
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-editorial-card-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_text_color }};
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .ai-editorial-card-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
  }

  .ai-editorial-card-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-width: 200px;
    max-height: 200px;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-editorial-empty-state-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    padding: 12px 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666;
    text-align: center;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-editorial-showcase-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_tablet }}, 1fr);
    }

    .ai-editorial-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.title_size }}px * 0.85);
    }

    .ai-editorial-card-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.subtitle_size }}px * 0.9);
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-editorial-showcase-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_mobile }}, 1fr);
    }

    .ai-editorial-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.title_size }}px * 0.75);
    }

    .ai-editorial-card-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.subtitle_size }}px * 0.85);
    }

    .ai-editorial-card-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: calc({{ block.settings.content_padding }}px * 0.75);
    }

    .ai-editorial-card-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.button_font_size }}px * 0.9);
      padding: calc({{ block.settings.button_padding_vertical }}px * 0.85) calc({{ block.settings.button_padding_horizontal }}px * 0.85);
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-editorial-showcase-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-editorial-showcase-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-editorial-showcase-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% for i in (1..3) %}
        {% liquid
          assign card_enabled_key = 'card_' | append: i | append: '_enabled'
          assign card_image_key = 'card_' | append: i | append: '_image'
          assign card_title_key = 'card_' | append: i | append: '_title'
          assign card_subtitle_key = 'card_' | append: i | append: '_subtitle'
          assign card_button_text_key = 'card_' | append: i | append: '_button_text'
          assign card_button_link_key = 'card_' | append: i | append: '_button_link'

          assign card_enabled = block.settings[card_enabled_key]
          assign card_image = block.settings[card_image_key]
          assign card_title = block.settings[card_title_key]
          assign card_subtitle = block.settings[card_subtitle_key]
          assign card_button_text = block.settings[card_button_text_key]
          assign card_button_link = block.settings[card_button_link_key]
        %}

        {% if card_enabled %}
          <div class="ai-editorial-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if card_image %}
              <img
                src="{{ card_image | image_url: width: 1200 }}"
                alt="{{ card_image.alt | escape }}"
                class="ai-editorial-card-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ card_image.width }}"
                height="{{ card_image.height }}"
              >
            {% else %}
              <div class="ai-editorial-card-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                <div class="ai-editorial-empty-state-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  Add an eyewear image for card {{ i }}
                </div>
              </div>
            {% endif %}

            <div class="ai-editorial-card-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>

            <div class="ai-editorial-card-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if card_title != blank %}
                <h3 class="ai-editorial-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ card_title }}</h3>
              {% endif %}

              {% if card_subtitle != blank %}
                <p class="ai-editorial-card-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ card_subtitle }}</p>
              {% endif %}

              {% if card_button_text != blank %}
                <a
                  href="{{ card_button_link }}"
                  class="ai-editorial-card-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                  {{ card_button_text }}
                </a>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

